y the original full backup and the incrementals since the VM was provis=
ioned.</font><br>
<br>
<font size=3D"2" face=3D"sans-serif">If it gets suspended, the VM charg=
e drops to the suspend rate of &nbsp;~$90 MRC. &nbsp;However, there is =
still a charge for the backup storage used. &nbsp;That will be the amou=
nt of the full backup that was created when the VM was originally provi=
sioned as well as any changes. &nbsp;</font><br>
<br>
<br>
